<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1038] Enhance CommonsHttpSolrServer to add docs in batch</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1038</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;add two methods to ComonsHttpSolrServer to facilitate batch upload of docs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void addAndCommit(Iterator&amp;lt;SolrInputDocument&amp;gt; docIter , SolrParams commitParams)  
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; SolrServerException, IOException 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This helps users to upload all docs in a single http request&lt;/p&gt;</description>
